Spain’s CNMV Extends Short-Selling Ban on Financial Stocks

-- B y   E m m a   R o s s - T h o m a s
-- 
2011-09-28T17:24:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/spain-s-cnmv-extends-short-selling-ban-on-financial-stocks.html
Spain ’s market regulator extended a
temporary ban on short-selling of financial stocks, it said in
an e-mailed statement today.  The ban, due to expire on Sept. 30, will remain in place
“until the market conditions allow it to be lifted,” the
regulator said in  Madrid .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emma Ross-Thomas at 
 erossthomas@bloomberg.net  